dc_description_s: This data represents community-based residential facility sites for Wisconsin in 2024. [This dataset contains locations and attributes of community-based residential facilities licensed by the state of Wisconsin. The data are used for planning, management and analysis by Wisconsin Department of Health Services staff and by other government agencies. For more information please visit the Wisconsin Department of Health Services website: https://www.dhs.wisconsin.gov/regulations/cbrf/introduction.htm]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://data.dhsgis.wi.gov/datasets/wi-dhs::wisconsin-community-based-residential-facilities/about
